"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-golf-1929652-Rory-McIlroy-Olympics-training-St-Andrews-Old-Course\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  In a bid to prep for the grand Paris Olympics, Rory McIlroy honed his skills at the legendary Old Course at St Andrews this week - making a nostaglic return to the very site where he came within mere shots of winning the 150th Open in 2022.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"grand Paris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 47, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The celebrated golfer was seen taking relaxed swings, while an eager crowd of approximately 100-200 spectators watched.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Viral clips from social media show McIlroy driving powerful shots across the 12th and 16th holes, interspersed with light-hearted chit-chat with fans.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One memorable exchange involved a particularly enthusiastic American fan, prompting McIlroy to jest with a cheeky retort: \\\"You are not gonna love us next year!\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999980202016148, \"rank\": 1.927702317185132e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"a playful nod to the intensity of the forthcoming 2025 Ryder Cup.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, McIlroy's immediate attention is on the Olympic men's tournament teeing off at Le Golf National on Thursday.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following several turbulent weeks, a commanding display in Paris could provide a much-needed boostwith the prospect of clinching Olympic gold adding to the allure.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 931, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.6598019564387555e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rewind to June, and McIlroy faced a bitter moment at the US Open, ceding a two-shot advantage in the latter stages to Bryson DeChambeau.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Post that heartbreak, the world's third-ranked golfer declared a brief hiatus from golf, only to re-emerge for the Genesis Scottish Open, where he claimed a respectable joint fourth finish.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy then suffered a frustrating Open at Royal Troon earlier this month, culminating in a dismal performance that saw him fail to make the cut.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Troon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Troon_Golf_Club\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After carding 78 and 74 over two rounds, McIlroy ended up an agonising 11 over-par, well adrift of the required mark.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His disastrous two-day total marked his poorest showing in a major since the Open Championship in 2013.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After his disappointing early departure from the Open, McIlroy openly admitted to reporters his lack of engagement following a catastrophic start.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think once I made the eight on the fourth hole, that was it,\\\" he confessed.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dismayed so early in the contest, McIlroy's thoughts turned pre-emptively to holiday plans, signalling his resignation from the competition: \\\"22 holes into the event and I am thinking about where I am going to go on vacation next week.\\\"\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the setback, \\\"Yeah, that was basically it.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, I knew from then I'd sort of resigned myself to the fact that I wasn't going to shoot, four, or five, under-par.\\\"\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quick to shake off the disappointment from Scotland, McIlroy alongside his spouse Erica Stoll and their young daughter Poppy jetted off to Portugal for a restorative family holiday.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2415, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8040073736996436, \"rank\": 0.2436451750223942, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\", \"score\": 0.9999999944589035, \"rank\": 5.541028392696437e-09, \"text\": \"Erica\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erica_Kane\"}, {\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984908002450029, \"rank\": 0.0013851449358794116, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fresh from his break by the Portuguese coasts, an invigorated McIlroy is set to embrace his second Olympic outing with aspirations of making Ireland beam with pride.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9073826434346969, \"rank\": 0.058039861682840095, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Despite narrowly missing out on a podium finish three years ago in Tokyo - where he lost the bronze in a dramatic seven-way playoff against CT Pan - McIlroy is undoubtedly seeking redemption on the grand Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999989002873598, \"rank\": 1.0997032879570987e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recenyly he has opened up about his choice to represent Ireland over Great Britain in the Olympics, explaining: \\\"As I said, previously, once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3254, \"end\": 3267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8928764820500191, \"rank\": 0.10176085907074378, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was I am going to play golf for the country or the nation that I have always played for through my junior and amateur days and now into the professional game.\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's Ireland.\\\"\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3743, \"end\": 3756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.323437008754762e-30, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3777, \"to\": 3844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3792, \"end\": 3805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.323437008754762e-30, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"